This is my custom build of suckless' tiling window manager, dwm. 

Required Packages:
    Mozilla Firefox(only mentioned in the rules)
    dmenu
    st
    rofi
    xorg
    git
    build-essential
    
Installation:
    Type these commands:
    git clone https://github.com/Agnomilted/dwm
    cd dwm
    make
    sudo make install       #Make sure you have the Xlib header files

Running Dwm:
    Add the line 
    exec dwm
    to the file .xinitrc to start using dwm using startx
